+/** Ordering guidelines:
+- modern optimized, multi-platform libraries: ffmpeg, gstreamer, Media SDK
+- platform specific universal SDK: WINRT, QTKIT/AVFOUNDATION, MSMF/VFW/DSHOW, V4L/V4L2
